Step 1. Apply for high-resolution images from Metropolitan Archival records.

> Data_Collection/Download_Image/ApplicationForHighResolution.ipynb

Step 2. Access high-resolution images by obtaining credential info from E-mail.

> Data_Collection/Download_Image/ExtractFromEmail.ipynb

Step 3. Crop images using a layout detection network. Split the image into pages or quadrants. Move images into Google Drive.

> Data_Collection/Download_Image/ExtractFromEmail.ipynb

Step 4. Apply NDLOCR to each crop.

> Data_Collection/NDLOCR/WorkingCopy_NDL_OCR.ipynb

Step 5. Detect columns and seperate them into positions/offices.

> Data_Collection/Download_Image/ExtractFromEmail.ipynb

Step 6. Get names and position by NLP.
